<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>TradeSphere</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home.css" />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Quantico:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=clash-display@400,500,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <link href="https://api.fontshare.com/v2/css?f[]=general-sans@400,500,700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      margin: 0;
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, pink 40%, red 100%);
    }

    header {
  background-color: #f8f9fa;
  padding: 10px 20px;
  border-bottom: 4px solid #d81b60;
  box-shadow: 0 1px 0 #b71c1c;
}

.header-container {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-between;
}

.header-logo {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

.header-logo img {
  height: 70px;
  margin-right: 10px;
  margin-bottom: 13px;
}

.header-logo h1 {
  font-family: 'Quantico', sans-serif;
}

.header-logo .trade {
  color: black;
  animation: colorChangeTrade .5s forwards;
}

.header-logo .sphere {
  color: black;
  animation: colorChangeSphere .5s forwards;
  animation-delay: .5s;
}

nav {
  margin-left: auto; /* Pushes the nav menu to the right */
}

nav ul {
  list-style: none;
  margin: 0;
  padding: 0;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
}

nav ul li {
  margin-left: 20px;
}

nav ul li a {
  text-decoration: none;
  color: #007bff;
  font-size: 1em;
}

nav ul li a:hover {
  text-decoration: underline;
}

    main {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: center;
      align-items: center;
      height: calc(100vh - 60px);
      text-align: center;
      background-color: transparent;
    }

    .main-content {
      max-width: 600px;
      padding: 20px;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      position: relative;
    }

    h2 {
      font-family: 'Clash Display', sans-serif;
      font-weight: bold;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      font-size: 6.0em;
      margin-bottom: -1px;
      color: #333;
      letter-spacing: 1.5px;
      line-height: 1;
      position: relative;
    }

    .line1, .line2 {
      white-space: nowrap;
      display: inline-block;
      opacity: 0; /* Hide initially for the stamp effect */
      animation: stampEffect 0.5s ease-in-out forwards;
    }

    .line1 {
      animation-delay: 1s; /* "TRADE SMARTER" slams first */
    }

    .line2 {
      animation-delay: 1.5s; /* "NOT HARDER" slams second */
    }

    @keyframes stampEffect {
      0% {
        transform: scale(4);
        opacity: 0;
      }
      50% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
      100% {
        transform: scale(1);
        opacity: 1;
      }
    }

    .highlighted-text {
      color: #fce4ec; /* Very light pink fill */
      text-shadow:
        1px 1px 0 #d81b60, /* Hot pink outline */
        -1px -1px 0 #d81b60,
        1px -1px 0 #d81b60,
        -1px 1px 0 #d81b60;
    }

    h3 {
      font-family: 'General Sans', sans-serif; 
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-weight: 400; 
      color: #480101;
      margin-bottom: 150px;
    }

    .signup-btn {
      position: relative;
      top: -100px;
      padding: 15px 20px;
      font-size: 1em;
      background-color: #add8e6;
      color: #4169e1;
      border: 2px solid #4169e1;
      border-radius: 5px;
      cursor: pointer;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .signup-btn:hover {
      background-color: #d81b60;
      color: #ffffff;
      border-color: #d81b60;
    }

  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <div class="header-container">
      <div class="header-logo">
        <img src="https://i.postimg.cc/9fcGJHNz/BULL-LOGO.png" alt="Bull Logo">
        <h1><span class="trade">Trade</span><span class="sphere">Sphere</span></h1>
      </div>
      <nav>
        <ul>
          <li><a href="/auth">Log In</a></li>
        </ul>
      </nav>
    </div>
  </header>
  <main>
    <div class="main-content">
      <h2>
        <span class="line1">TRADE <span class="highlighted-text">SMARTER,</span></span><br>
        <span class="line2">NOT <span class="highlighted-text2">HARDER.</span>
      </h2>
      <h3>Track and manage your trades with ease.<br>Create portfolios, record trades, and stay organizedâ€”<br>all in one simple, powerful tool.</h3>
      <a href="/auth"><button id="signupButton" class="signup-btn">Sign Up for Free</button></a>
    </div>
  </main>
</body>
</html>